==== INSTALL ====

For Linux/Unix:
sudo python setup.py install

Windows:
python ./sharez.in


==== RUN ====

To run Sharez simply type
 sharez
or go to your menu Applications -> Utilitys.


==== USEAGE ====

Drop a destination folder in the "Drop here."-field. All files and folder that
should be coppied in there can now be added using Drag and Drop. After pressing
'Apply' all files are coppied using rsync. You can watch the process under 'Jobs'.

